{"tid":725180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★劏房戶上街冀改善住屋： 曾「伴屍」多日懵然不知","createTime":"2018-07-01T14:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T11:50:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd51d1d41c84fa2c5326b32ad4f3346ca075502b","tid":725180,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"香港房屋問題嚴重，雖然行政長官林鄭月娥日前推出新房策，但仍有不少人選擇七一上街表達不滿。有劏房戶指出，苦候公屋上樓至今已11年，惟未有任何消息，樓上不單經常出現火災，更<span style=\"color: gold;\">曾「伴屍」多日卻懞然不知，直至強烈屍臭味傳出才發現鄰居離世</span>，令她每日惶恐度日。她批評政府無能，無法替一眾劏戶房解決困境。<br />\n<br />\n有年輕人更指出，由於無力置業，現時一家六口屈居於400呎的公屋內，又指在房間內每人連一個階磚位也沒有，她批評：「我們（年輕人）每天努力工作，但一個有瓦遮頭地方都換不到！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">年輕人：努力後也換不到有瓦遮頭的地方<br />\n</span><br />\n黃小姐表示，香港房屋問題嚴重，故特意上街遊行表達訴求。她指出，現時一家六口居於400呎的公屋內，三個人要共用一間房間，連「碌架床」亦要特別訂做成三層，她稱：「一個人連一個階磚位也沒有。」<br />\n<br />\n她指出，過去曾與兄弟姊妹計劃搬家，惟200呎的單位月租卻達萬元，即使在職人士亦難以負擔，加上現時樓價高企，他們只能望塵莫及，「唔好話置業，就連年輕人要獨立自主都成問題，我們每天努力工作，但要搵一個有瓦遮頭的地方都換不到。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/205652/%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%86%80%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E4%BD%8F%E5%B1%8B-%E6%9B%BE-%E4%BC%B4%E5%B1%8D-%E5%A4%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%87%B5%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F205652%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E6%259B%25BE-%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E5%25B1%258D-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2587%25B5%25E7%2584%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5&d=f3q2cijn%2B40Qtzyc%2FfPqZ9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4185519d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/205652/%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%86%80%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E4%BD%8F%E5%B1%8B-%E6%9B%BE-%E4%BC%B4%E5%B1%8D-%E5%A4%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%87%B5%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5</a>"},{"pid":"aaa6c32aed79661bd58434e7a5e6d1b06951f446","tid":725180,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png&h=d3057e31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8079c30408383d23dcda5c3ed21f93e94b8a198","tid":725180,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b9201306ac1bfeef79d55207e73d9396595c37f","tid":725180,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"林鄭點解會推平居屋 完全損人不利己<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bnJyvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bnJyvS</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下班樓奴 幾撚想供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6546af606919b43e66125b9a76856ea5dfe7757d","tid":725180,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f83477a3aaf2e352120feaf087adff303297a67e","tid":725180,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime